released at their semiannual retreat in hot springs va a posh 
resort town 
the april advance in the labor departments producer price index 
for finished goods one stop short of retail followed an identical 
04 percent gain in march and 1 percent jumps in january and 
february 
because of the steep rises early in the year wholesale prices 
increased at a 9 percent annual rate in the first four months of 
1989 thats more than double last years wholesale inflation of 4 
percent and four times the 22 percent rate in 1987 
however economists said much but not all of the 
acceleration this year is attributable to a onetime shock from a 
