showed moderation intermediate goods rose 04 percent in april 
following a 07 percent jump in march crude goods rose 06 percent 
following a 23 percent gain 
an example of the three processing levels would be wholesale 
bread at the finished level flour at the intermediate and wheat at 
the crude 
